
/* Additional code fields for the following:
1) Ading additional Admin Approver for new member requests.
2) Adding "Phone" as new field in Admin, Directory & Profile pages
3) Adding "Kennel Name: as new field in Admin, Directory & Profile pages
4) Adding "Additional Info- Volunteer Interests" as new field in Admin & Profile pages
5) Adding "Member Type": as new field in Admin only 
6) Adding "Newsletters & ECSCA Info Delivery Method" as new field in Admin & Profile pages
7) "Online Membership Enrollment Date" in Admin, Directory & Profile pages.
8) "Club Membership Start Year" in Admin, Directory & Profile pages.
9) "Primary Volunteer Event Type" in Admin, Directory & Profile pages.
10) "Secondary Volunteer Event Type" in Admin, Directory & Profile pages.
*/










